  .m-b-20.faq-container
      .row
        .col-md-8
          h3.heading Rewardners International
          p
            | Through the platform of Rewardners you can bring to your country all the Rewardners benefits. With our international program you can receive full support and help for all the local businesses in your country to start using Rewardners within the Network of Cities and Countries which Rewardners expands constantly.
